1(£=== CLI Unit Converter ===):
[value]=;(£Enter numeric value: ):
[from]=;(£From unit (cm/m/km): ):
[to]=;(£To unit (cm/m/km): ):
[value]$f:
[inMeters]=^0^:
2([from]..£cm){[inMeters]=|`value/100|}:
2([from]..£m){[inMeters]=`value}:
2([from]..£km){[inMeters]=|`value*1000|}:
[out]=^0^:
2([to]..£cm){[out]=|`inMeters*100|}:
2([to]..£m){[out]=`inMeters}:
2([to]..£km){[out]=|`inMeters/1000|}:
1(£Converted value):
1([out]):
